data.description:
2 Story / Roof Top Deck with Valley Views - TRIUMPH Property Management in  Las Vegas, Nevada presents!
 A  2 story house on 6567 Conquistador St. in  Las Vegas , NV.
This home is in the Northwest with shopping, schools, parks and easy 215 access nearby.
The home features 4 bedrooms, great room, open kitchen, family room, 2 car garage and roof top deck.
The entry foyer has a tile floor, vaulted ceiling and a chandelier.
The great room has carpeting, window blinds and a ceiling fan with light.
The kitchen and Ding area has a tile floor, center island breakfast bar, granite counters, custom cabinets and stainless appliances.
The full bathroom has a 1 piece tub shower combo.
The downstairs bedroom has carpeting and a ceiling fan with light.
The attached 2 car garage has an auto door opener, water conditioner and direct entry to the home.
The upstairs is carpeted and has a family room , 3 bedrooms, laundry room and 2 full bathrooms.
The family room is upstairs and has a ceiling fan with light.
The master bedroom has a ceiling fan with light.
The master bathroom has a tile floor, double sink vanity, walk in closet, separate shower, tub and a water closet.
The full 2nd bathroom has a tile floor, large vanity and a water closet with a 1 piece tub shower combo.
The laundry room has a tile floor, storage cabinets and the washer and dryer included in the rent.
The 2nd bedroom has a ceiling fan with light and a walk in closet.
The 3rd bedroom has a ceiling fan with light and a walk in closet.
The home has a roof top deck  with mountain and valley views.
This 4  bedroom 3 bath house  with  2681 SF is available now for rent.
Contact one of Triumphs friendly Real Estate Agents to view this property.

*Sorry NO SECTION 8 accepted 

"Contact one of our friendly Real Estate Agents TODAY for IMMEDIATE SHOWING either via phone (702) 550-2222 

Or visit our website: www.vegasrentnow.com for a list of all of our vacancies 

When submitting an application the following is required, 
- Rental application filled in ALL FIELDS. No Blanks 
- Application fee - $65 per adult [NON REFUNDABLE] 
- Proof of funds i.e. Bank Statements 
- Verification of Employment or Pay stubs 
- Previous landlord reference or contact number including fax or e-mail.

(RLNE3275509)
